      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this beauty in person. It\u2019s in absolutely incredible shape\u2014honestly, it feels like it just rolled right off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and it is spotless inside and out. It drives like an absolute dream and still has that fresh car smell. I'm really looking for a good home for it, and I know you're going to love it as much as I do! \u2728",
