    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "This 2004 BMW M3 (E46) represents a pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering. Power is derived from the S54 inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a high-revving 8,000 RPM redline. This unit has undergone comprehensive preventative maintenance, including a Beisan Systems VANOS overhaul and rod bearing replacement to ensure reciprocating assembly longevity. The 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox provides crisp engagement, feeding power through a variable M differential lock. The chassis is structurally sound with documented subframe reinforcement, maintaining factory torsional rigidity. Finished in Carbon Black, the exterior remains in concours condition, while the suspension retains its original geometry for an unadulterated analog driving experience. No deferred maintenance; a turn-key collector-grade specimen.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 45
    },
    {
