      "description": "Offering a truly exceptional vehicle that presents in showroom condition. This car has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, resulting in a deep, mirror-like paint finish completely free of stone chips, swirl marks, or blemishes. The interior is a masterclass in preservation; the premium leather remains soft and matte, the carpets are spotless, and every electronic component operates with factory precision. Under the hood, the engine bay is detailed to a concours standard, backed by a comprehensive folder of every service record since new. The undercarriage is equally pristine, reflecting a life of fair-weather use only. This is not just a used car; it is a collector-grade example for the buyer who accepts nothing less than perfection.",
