      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this beauty in person. It\u2019s honestly like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014absolutely pristine and sparkling! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and it drives just as smooth as it looks. No scratches, no dents, and the interior is still smelling fresh. I'm looking for a new home for it where it\u2019ll be just as loved. Drop me a message and come take a look\u2014you definitely won't be disappointed!",
